(67. Keep the local bot route public so guests can access it.) Tj
T*
(68. Add logout functionality that destroys the session.) Tj
T*
(69. Handle invalid login attempts with clean messages.) Tj
T*
(70. Test the full register-login-logout flow in the browser.) Tj
T*
