T*
(PHASE 8: GAME DATA MODELS) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(71. Create `src/modules/games/game.model.js` to store completed match results.) Tj
T*
(72. Add fields such as `mode`, `players`, `winner`, `moves`, `duration`, and `status`.) Tj
T*
(73. Create a `chat.model.js` for direct or room messages.) Tj
T*
(74. Create a `friend.model.js` or store friend relationships in the user model.) Tj
T*
(75. Create a `leaderboard` strategy based on rating, wins, or score.) Tj
T*
(76. Decide whether leaderboard data is calculated live or cached in MongoDB.) Tj
T*
(77. Add indexes for fields used in sorting and lookups.) Tj
T*
(78. Create seed data scripts only if you need sample users and matches.) Tj
T*
(79. Keep schema logic lightweight; move business logic to services.) Tj
T*
(80. Test that all models save and read correctly from MongoDB.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PHASE 9: LOCAL BOT GAME FIRST) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(81. Start with one game only, for example Tic-Tac-Toe, Connect 4, or simple Chess-lite.) Tj
T*
(82. Create `game.engine.js` for the core game rules.) Tj
T*
(83. Create `game.state.js` to define the starting state and update rules.) Tj
T*
(84. Create `bot.engine.js` with simple AI for local guest play.) Tj
T*
(85. Build the browser UI for the game board in vanilla JS.) Tj
T*
(86. Add click handlers and render updates in `public/js/game/client.js`.) Tj
T*
(87. Make the guest local game work fully without login.) Tj
T*
(88. Prevent illegal moves in both frontend and backend logic.) Tj
T*
(89. Save local-game results only if you want analytics; otherwise keep them temporary.) Tj
T*
(90. Do a full manual test of the bot game from start to finish.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PHASE 10: WEBSOCKET AND MULTIPLAYER FOUNDATION) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(91. Attach a WebSocket server to the same HTTP server.) Tj
T*
(92. Create `src/sockets/index.js` to initialize and manage connections.) Tj
T*
(93. Authenticate WebSocket users using the existing session or a secure token.) Tj
T*
(94. Track connected users and their socket IDs in memory.) Tj
T*
(95. Create a room system for lobbies and active matches.) Tj
T*
(96. Add basic events like `joinLobby`, `createMatch`, `joinMatch`, `playerMove`, and) Tj
T*
