T*
(97. Broadcast game state updates to all players in a room.) Tj
T*
(98. Reuse the same `game.engine.js` rules for multiplayer validation.) Tj
T*
(99. Save the completed multiplayer match to MongoDB and update leaderboard stats.) Tj
T*
(100. After multiplayer works, build the extra features in this order: chat, friends,) Tj
T*
(leaderboard polishing, notifications, tests, security hardening, and deployment.) Tj
T*
